schema.title: IMember
schema.description: Interface representing a member with personal details and hobby information

age.description: Age of the member, must be at least 20 and less than 100

created_at.description: Timestamp when the member record was created

updated_at.description: Timestamp when the member record was last updated

deleted_at.description: Timestamp when the member record was deleted, or null if not deleted
